Corp. plans to introduce the production line in Shanghai. Bidding
on the production line is under way for manufacturers from around
the world.
</P>
<P>
This DVD production line can also be used for producing CDs,
VCDs, and CD-ROMs, said Wang Hao, deputy director of the National
Engineering Research Center, adding that the popularity of DVD
will promote development of digital audio and video products.
</P>
